ACL in Router. ACL - to control access of device in a network


When we do ACL in router it becomes Security device. Usually we do ACL in Edge router.

ACL list type:
1. Standard: control source ip only, can not control destination. (It will total permit for outside networks.)
2. Extended: Control source as well as destination. 


>>Configuration of Standard List 
1. Create list
#ip access-list standard LAN-WAN (given name for inside to outside)
#permit host 192.168.100.1      (To allow single host)
#permit any                     (To permit any)    
#permit 192.168.100.0 0.0.0.255 (To permit whole network with wildcard bits)

2. To implemet policy on inside interface
#interface eth0/0 (inside interface)
#ip access-group LAN-WAN IN

After this only pc1 is permitted to google and rest is blocked.

